<i>noun</i>: 피신 [피ː신] <i>verb</i>: 피신하다 [피ː신하다], 피난하다 [피ː난하다], 토끼다 [토끼다], 들고뛰다 [들고뛰다], 도피하다 [도피하다], 도망하다 [도망하다], 도망치다 [도망치다], 도망가다 [도망가다], 내빼다 [내ː빼다], 내뛰다 [내ː뛰다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>피신 [피ː신]</dt><br>
<dd>escape; flight; flee</dd><br>
<dd>위험을 피해 안전한 곳으로 몸을 숨김.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of hiding oneself in a safe place, away from danger.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>피신하다 [피ː신하다]</dt><br>
<dd>escape; flee; take refugee</dd><br>
<dd>위험을 피해 안전한 곳으로 몸을 숨기다.</dd><br>
<dd>To hide in a safe area, away from danger.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>피난하다 [피ː난하다]</dt><br>
<dd>take refuge; be evacuated; flee</dd><br>
<dd>전쟁, 자연재해 등의 재난을 피해 멀리 도망가다.</dd><br>
<dd>To run away far from a catastrophe such as a war, natural disaster, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>토끼다 [토끼다]</dt><br>
<dd>flee</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 도망가다.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) To run away.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>들고뛰다 [들고뛰다]</dt><br>
<dd>flee; run away</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 달아나다.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) To run away.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>도피하다 [도피하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. escape; flee</dd><br>
<dd>무엇을 피해 도망가다.</dd><br>
<dd>To run away from something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. escape</dd><br>
<dd>해야 하거나 맞서야 할 일을 애써 외면하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To turn away from what one has to do or confront.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>도망하다 [도망하다]</dt><br>
<dd>escape; make off; flee</dd><br>
<dd>피하거나 쫓기어 달아나다.</dd><br>
<dd>To run away when chased by or in order to avoid someone or something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>도망치다 [도망치다]</dt><br>
<dd>escape; make off; flee</dd><br>
<dd>피하거나 쫓기어 달아나다.</dd><br>
<dd>To run away when chased by or in order to avoid someone or something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>도망가다 [도망가다]</dt><br>
<dd>escape; make off; flee</dd><br>
<dd>피하거나 쫓기어 달아나다.</dd><br>
<dd>To run away from something or someone because one is either chased or wants to avoid it or him/her.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>내빼다 [내ː빼다]</dt><br>
<dd>flee; run away</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 도망가다.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) To run away.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>내뛰다 [내ː뛰다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. run out; dart off</dd><br>
<dd>힘껏 앞으로 뛰어가다.</dd><br>
<dd>To run forward in a full strength.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flee; run away</dd><br>
<dd>빠르게 도망쳐 달아나다.</dd><br>
<dd>To run away quickly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>